  <brief_title>Atrial Fibrillation Recurrence Following Cardioversion: the Role of Clinical Factors and Alpha Defensin Levels</brief_title>
  <official_title>Atrial Fibrillation Recurrence Following Cardioversion: the Role of Clinical Factors and Alpha Defensin Levels</official_title>
